text: Marie-Angéline Colson (born 21 May 1976) is a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Clermont-Ferrand
